comments: Murray (ATL) extends his leg as part of his shooting motion and marginal contact occurs with Stevens (MEM) as he contests the jump shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Murray's (ATL) shot attempt does not contact the rim and the shot clock expires.
Stevens (MEM) slightly extends his hand toward Murray (ATL) and marginal contact occurs as Stevens releases away to roll.
Williams Jr. (MEM) briefly engages with Bogdanovic (ATL) in the lane.
Hunter (ATL) and Williams Jr. (MEM) come together in transition and the marginal contact does not dislodge Williams Jr. from his defensive position.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) swipes down and initiates contact to Bogdanovic's (ATL) left knee, causing him to trip.
Stevens (MEM) blocks the shot attempt and is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Capela (ATL) initiates contact to Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) wrist that affects his shot attempt in the lane.
Williams Jr. (MEM) commits a take foul on Capela (ATL).
